data.description:
Located in the well desired Morningside subdivision, it is spacious and bright.
This stunning 2 bed, 2 bath condo is the perfect place to call home! From the moment you enter, you'll be greeted by sleek laminate flooring, an open floorplan, and an abundance of natural light. The well-appointed kitchen features wood cabinets, ample cabinet space, and a pantry, making it the perfect place to cook and entertain. The thoughtfully designed open floorplan is ideal for gatherings, with a dining area, large living room, and space for more. The primary suite features an expansive layout, extra room for a desk or sitting area, a large walk-in closet with custom built-ins, an en-suite 3/4 bath, and access to the screened-in lanai. The second bedroom is also generously sized, with ample closet space.
 This condo also offers a number of other amenities, including: In-unit laundry assigned garage space and storage unit. Access to community amenities such as a fitness center, clubhouse, indoor and outdoor pools, and elevators Near shopping, restaurants, I-25, the DTC, and downtown Denver, this condo has it all! Schedule a showing today and see for yourself why this condo is the perfect place to call home!
